wdtools - WorkDiary Tools
=========================

This is a set of tools to make a statistic from a plain text work diary in
specific format.

Building
--------

To build wdtools simply type make. You may want to change config.mk depending
on your system and config.h depending on your needs.

Running wdtools
---------------

Simply put your work diary to a standard input of stat, punch or wrkhr with
selected parameters. The result is printed to the standard output. Read man
pages for more informations about parameters.

